{
  "1": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Pay attention to what Yahweh will say:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Micah says to Yahweh, \"Stand up in court and accuse the Israelites.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Allow the hills and mountains to hear what you will say.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "2": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The mountains must listen carefully to what Yahweh says about his people, so they can be witnesses.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Indeed, Yahweh has many things to accuse his people Israel about.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "3": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "He says this: \"My people, what have I done to cause trouble for you ?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "What have I done to cause you to experience difficulties?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Answer me!\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "4": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I did great things for your ancestors;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I brought them out of Egypt;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I rescued them from that land where they were slaves.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I sent Moses to lead them,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and his older brother Aaron and his older sister Miriam.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "5": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "My people, think about when Balak, the king of Moab, requested Beor's son Balaam to curse your ancestors,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and think about what Balaam replied.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Think about how your ancestors crossed the Jordan River miraculously while they were traveling from Acacia to Gilgal.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Think about those things in order that you may know that I, Yahweh, do what is right.\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "6": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The Israelite people ask, \"What shall we bring to Yahweh who lives in heaven\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "when we come to him and bow down before him?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Should we bring calves that are a year old\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "that will be offerings that will be killed and completely burned on the altar?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "7": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Would Yahweh be pleased if we offered to him a thousand rams\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and ten thousand streams of olive oil?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Should we offer our firstborn children to be sacrifices\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "to pay for the sins that we have committed?\"\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "8": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "No, because he has shown each of us what is good to do;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "he has shown us what he requires each of us to do:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "he wants us to do what is just and to love to act mercifully toward others,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and he wants us to live humbly while we fellowship with him, our God.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "9": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "God says this: \"I am Yahweh, so if you are wise, you should honor me.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I am calling out to you people of Jerusalem to tell you this:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "The armies that will destroy your city are coming,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "so pay careful attention to me, the one who is causing them to punish you with my rod.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "10": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "You wicked people have filled your homes with valuable things\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "that you acquired by cheating others.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "You use false measures when you buy and sell things.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Those are things that I hate.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "11": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "You do not think that I should say nothing about people who use scales that do not weigh correctly,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and who use weights that are not accurate, do you?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "12": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The rich people among you always act violently to get money from poor people.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "All of the people in Jerusalem are liars,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and they always deceive people.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "13": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Therefore, I have already begun to get rid of you,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "to ruin you because of the sins that you have committed.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "14": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Soon you will eat food, but you will not have enough to satisfy you;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "your stomachs will still feel as though they are empty.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "You will try to save up money,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "but you will be able to save nothing,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "because I will send your enemies to take it from you in wars.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "15": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "You will plant crops,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "but you will not harvest anything.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "You will press olives,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "but others, not you, will use the olive oil.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "You will trample on the grapes and make wine from the juice,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "but others, not you, will drink the wine.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "16": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Those things will happen to you because you obey only the wicked laws of King Omri,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and you do the terrible things that King Ahab and his descendants commanded.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "So I will destroy your country,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and I will cause the other people groups to despise you, my own people.\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      }
    ]
  },
  "front": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "p",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "paragraph"
      }
    ]
  }
}